Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Holdings - Wikipedia





















 






Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Holdings

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Holdings, Inc.
三井住友トラスト・ホールディングス株式会社





Type

Public KK


Traded as
TYO: 8309


Industry
Financial services


Founded
2002; 15 years ago (2002) (as Chuo Mitsui Trust Holdings, Inc.)


Headquarters
Tokyo, Japan



Area served

Worldwide



Key people

Kazuo Tanabe (President)


