Cayman Islands













Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Bank (U.S.A.) Limited
 


overview

Deposit Guarantee
Locations



  


















Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Bank is a Japanese financial services company, 
specializing in asset and wealth management, real estate management, corporate finance.Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Bank (U.S.A.) Limited has Category B banking license number 
100101 issued by the Cayman Islands Monetary Authority. This type of 
license allows Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Bank (U.S.A.) Limited to conduct banking and trustee operations 
with non-residents and domestic banking business with other Cayman Islands 
licenced entities.  




Address190 Elgin Avenue, KY1-1108, Grand Cayman, Cayman IslandsP.O. Box1353 

Bank CategoryCategory B (Banking & Trust)  
 


 

Deposit Guarantee0 KYD  
 
 
 

Similar Banks
 Bank Hapoalim (Cayman) Limited Bank Leumi Le Israel B.M. Wing Hang Bank (Cayman) Ltd




 
 


Country Information
 
Economy and Banking Sector of the Cayman Islands
 
	List of Banks in the Cayman Islands
 

Related Articles
Banking Sector of the Cayman IslandsFATCA and European countries 




Deposit Guarantee



Deposit Guarantee




No


Deposit Guarantee Schemes compensate certain deposits 
held by depositors of a bank that becomes unable to meet its obligations.There is no deposit guarantee scheme in the Cayman Islands.In the case of Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Bank (U.S.A.) Limited failure its depositors will no be paid out 
any compensation.




European Presence: 3 banks in 3 countries
This bank operates in the following European countries 
		and selected dependent territories of the European countries:
Cayman Islands (this bank) Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Bank (U.S.A.) Limited (Grand Cayman)
Luxembourg Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Bank (Luxembourg) S.A. (Howald)
United Kingdom Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Bank Limited (London)




 
 











 















